did.abstract: The records consist of correspondence, financial statements, contracts, reports, minutes, exams, papers, lectures, statistics, and student and personnel files documenting the Yale Department of Religious Studies. Topics include committees and councils; religious services; faculty; student performance and activity; curriculum and course development; admissions; financial aid; fellowships and scholarships; and dissertations.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The records consist of correspondence, financial statements, contracts, reports, minutes, exams, papers, lectures, statistics, and student and personnel files documenting the Yale Department of Religious Studies. Topics include committees and councils; religious services; faculty; student performance and activity; curriculum and course development; admissions; financial aid; fellowships and scholarships; and dissertations.
